PLATYSCELIDAE 
<bibRefCitation author="Bate" box="[500,631,1628,1654]" pageId="98" pageNumber="99" refString="Bate, C. S. (1862) Catalogue of the specimens of Amphipodous Crustacea in the collection of the British Museum. British Museum, Natural History, London, 399 pp., plates 1 - 58." type="book chapter" year="1862">Bate, 1862</bibRefCitation>
